14:57.331 --> 14:59.507
if this goes to appeal.

15:00.725 --> 15:02.249
Put it behind us for now.

15:02.292 --> 15:04.294
We've got enough to worry about
with Lindell.

15:04.338 --> 15:06.383
He'll want to distance himself
from any scandal.

15:06.427 --> 15:09.082
That's great. Lindell.
Guy's wanted me gone

15:09.125 --> 15:11.171
since he got here.

15:11.214 --> 15:13.260
Now is his shot.

15:13.303 --> 15:14.914
Master Chief Hayes
retired from operating,

15:14.957 --> 15:16.306
then asked to return
to field duty.

15:16.350 --> 15:18.004
Do you know why?

15:18.047 --> 15:20.615
He believed he would have the
most impact on the battlefield.

15:20.658 --> 15:23.009
Couldn't stay out
of the fight, could he?

15:23.052 --> 15:24.880
Did you have
any reservations

15:24.924 --> 15:27.361
about reinstating
Master Chief Hayes as Bravo 1?

15:27.404 --> 15:30.320
His performance mitigated
any of my concerns.

15:30.364 --> 15:32.670
