where you refer to Master Chief
Hayes as a "renegade."

15:41.984 --> 15:43.464
So, in your opinion,

15:43.507 --> 15:44.856
does the Master Chief

15:44.900 --> 15:46.423
play by his own rules?

15:53.691 --> 15:57.695
I was referring to his tactics,
not his character.

15:57.739 --> 16:00.524
While it's true the Master
Chief doesn't always do things

16:00.568 --> 16:02.657
the way I would like...

16:02.700 --> 16:05.312
I'm loathe to imagine what the
war on terror would look like

16:05.355 --> 16:07.618
without him
at the tip of the spear.

16:07.662 --> 16:09.969
In all my years in the Teams,

16:10.012 --> 16:12.101
I've come across
no finer operator

16:12.145 --> 16:14.495
than Master Chief Hayes.

16:14.538 --> 16:16.540
♪

16:21.676 --> 16:23.504
Appreciate you cleaning
yourself up, SO1 Quinn.

16:23.547 --> 16:25.245
Navy gave us relaxed
grooming standards

16:25.288 --> 16:26.942
so we could stay mission ready.

16:26.986 --> 16:28.465
You like

16:28.509 --> 16:31.860
going after guys for following
the rules, don't you? Hmm?

16:31.903 --> 16:33.253
When you passed the deceased
in the hallway,

16:33.296 --> 16:35.342
did you see a gun on his person
or on the ground?

16:35.385 --> 16:37.866
I didn't. No.

16:37.909 --> 16:39.172
No, sir, I did not.

16:39.215 --> 16:40.738
But I wasn't looking for one.

16:40.782 --> 16:42.262
You never even entered
the building,

16:42.305 --> 16:44.351
yet in your deposition,
you allege Master Chief Hayes

16:44.394 --> 16:45.352
followed the ROEs?

16:45.395 --> 16:47.180
If Master Chief Hayes shot
a man,

16:47.223 --> 16:49.138
that man had a weapon
or was a direct threat.

16:49.182 --> 16:50.357
You saw the victim enter
the building.

16:50.400 --> 16:51.532
Did you see him holding the gun

16:51.575 --> 16:52.881
Master Chief Hayes describes?

16:52.924 --> 16:54.970
One guy had an AK slung
over his shoulder.

16:55.014 --> 16:56.928
Other guy could have had
a concealed weapon.

16:56.972 --> 16:58.713
FLORES:
But you didn't see the
weapon on the victim?

16:58.756 --> 17:01.368
It was your regular Jihad Joe
working for AKM.

17:01.411 --> 17:02.891
The same terrorist

17:02.934 --> 17:04.806
that blew up
12 servicemen

17:04.849 --> 17:07.461
in Baghdad.Answer the question,
Petty Officer.

17:09.463 --> 17:11.334
No, I didn't.

17:11.378 --> 17:12.466
Four eagle-eyed sharpshooters,

17:12.509 --> 17:15.034
and not one of them
spotted a gun.

17:15.077 --> 17:16.252
Have you ever questioned

17:16.296 --> 17:17.993
Bravo 1's decision-making
on a mission?

17:18.037 --> 17:20.648
We've all had
our difference of opinions.

17:20.691 --> 17:22.389
But I trust

17:22.432 --> 17:24.695
Master Chief Hayes more
than anyone to get us home.

17:24.739 --> 17:25.957
Has anyone discussed going
"shields up"

17:26.001 --> 17:27.046
to protect your team leader?

17:27.089 --> 17:28.395
No, sir.

17:28.438 --> 17:30.397
No member of Bravo
would stand by

17:30.440 --> 17:32.703
and support a brother
if he committed a war crime.

17:32.747 --> 17:34.923
None of you saw
this elusive gun,

17:34.966 --> 17:38.666
yet you all assert, under oath,
that Chief Hayes is innocent.

17:38.709 --> 17:40.276
If he made that mistake,

17:40.320 --> 17:42.626
he'd own up to it.Really?

17:42.670 --> 17:44.541
Can you name one instance
of Master Chief Hayes

17:44.585 --> 17:46.543
owning up to an error
he made in the field?

17:48.328 --> 17:50.504
Nothing comes to mind.

17:55.900 --> 17:57.380
Teammates painted
a picture of you

17:57.424 --> 17:59.078
as someone who's always in
control on the battlefield.

17:59.121 --> 18:00.383
I'm not sure
they swayed the panel.

18:00.427 --> 18:01.689
Only two members
have seen combat.

18:01.732 --> 18:03.734
The rest of them
don't know what it's like

18:03.778 --> 18:06.433
outside the wire.Which is why Chief
Warrant Officer Perry,

18:06.476 --> 18:08.478
as an officer and operator,
is our best option

18:08.522 --> 18:10.480
to appeal to them.Or the best option

18:10.524 --> 18:12.613
to put the final nail
in my coffin.

18:12.656 --> 18:14.615
[clears throat][gavel bangs twice]

18:14.658 --> 18:16.530
SERGEANT AT ARMS:
Court will now come to order.

18:16.573 --> 18:18.358
Is the government prepared
to proceed?

18:18.401 --> 18:20.099
Yes, Your Honor.

18:20.142 --> 18:21.361
Call your next witness.

18:21.404 --> 18:22.492
The government calls

18:22.536 --> 18:23.537
Chief Warrant Officer
Raymond Perry

18:23.580 --> 18:24.712
to the stand.

18:24.755 --> 18:26.757
