18:36.941 --> 18:38.595
RAY: The night
before the mission.

18:38.639 --> 18:40.815
FLORES:
When did Master Chief
Hayes learn this?

18:40.858 --> 18:42.425
The next morning.

18:42.469 --> 18:44.427
Did Master Chief Hayes
pressure you

18:44.471 --> 18:47.430
into launching an opwithout approval from Jordan?No.

18:47.474 --> 18:50.172
No?

18:50.216 --> 18:52.914
In your deposition, when
asked if Master Chief Hayes

18:52.957 --> 18:55.177
was eager to pursue the
op, you answered yes.

18:55.221 --> 18:58.746
Yes, he wanted to move;
no, he didn't pressure me.

18:59.834 --> 19:01.575
The timeline of events
indicates that

19:01.618 --> 19:03.751
as soon as Master Chief Hayes
knew of your connection

19:03.794 --> 19:06.057
