actionable intel that morning.

19:09.104 --> 19:11.585
You're saying the Master Chief's
knowledge of Raqqa Jacques

19:11.628 --> 19:14.327
and the launch of this op
was just a coincidence?

19:14.370 --> 19:15.328
Yes, sir.

19:15.371 --> 19:17.808
Time was of the essence.

19:17.852 --> 19:20.376
How many S.A. missions
have you led as warrant officer?

19:21.464 --> 19:23.118
Two.

19:23.162 --> 19:24.989
FLORES:
You were held captive
for six days and subjected

19:25.033 --> 19:27.427
to extreme physical and
psychological torture.

19:27.470 --> 19:28.732
I'm sure no one
in this courtroom

19:28.776 --> 19:30.169
would blame you for bending

19:30.212 --> 19:31.561
to the will of someone you trust

19:31.605 --> 19:32.693
if they promised you
retribution.

19:32.736 --> 19:33.998
Is that a question, sir?

19:34.042 --> 19:36.392
Must be difficult...
to suddenly act as OIC

19:36.436 --> 19:39.439
to a man you have been
subordinate to for 13 years.

19:39.482 --> 19:41.702
As much as I respect
Master Chief Hayes,

19:41.745 --> 19:44.139
I respect
the chain of command more.

19:44.183 --> 19:45.880
It was my decision

19:45.923 --> 19:47.403
to take the op kinetic.

19:47.447 --> 19:49.013
The mission
was a success,

19:49.057 --> 19:50.276
as was the follow-on.

19:50.319 --> 19:51.668
And for the record...

19:51.712 --> 19:54.105
I killed Raqqa Jacques,

19:54.149 --> 19:55.716
not Jason Hayes.

20:02.505 --> 20:04.507
No further questions.

20:06.596 --> 20:07.945
Your Honor,

20:07.989 --> 20:09.773
given that Chief Warrant Officer
Perry's testimony

20:09.817 --> 20:12.123
nullifies the revenge motive
for murder,

20:12.167 --> 20:14.430
I propose a motion to
dismiss all charges.

20:15.823 --> 20:19.043
I will dismiss the charge
of premeditated murder.

20:19.087 --> 20:20.871
But the members

20:20.915 --> 20:23.222
could still find for
involuntary manslaughter.

20:25.876 --> 20:27.878
The witness may
be excused.

20:31.012 --> 20:33.014
♪

20:45.809 --> 20:48.247
Ray had your six
after all.
Mm-hmm.

20:48.290 --> 20:50.379
Losing motive puts a big hole
in the prosecution's case.

20:50.423 --> 20:52.381
But the involuntary
manslaughter,

20:52.425 --> 20:54.818
this boots me
off the team,

20:54.862 --> 20:57.168
gets me ten years.

20:57.212 --> 20:59.258
Still, there's no gun.

20:59.301 --> 21:01.434
Our expert witness will poke
holes in the video evidence.

21:01.477 --> 21:03.262
Expert witness?
